dc_title_s: Johnson's New York; by Johnson & Browning.; New York
dc_description_s: Relief shown by hachures. Shows county boundaries and township boundaries. Prime meridians: Greenwich and Washington. Map within decorative border. In upper margin: 27. Insets: Oswego -- Albany -- Troy -- Vicinity of New York -- Buffalo -- Rochester -- Syracuse. 1 map: hand col.; 42 x 60 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
